{"text_id":143712,"tokens":["The"," grade"," point"," average"," requirement"," for"," sports"," and"," extracurricular"," activities"," is"," a"," topic"," of"," ongoing"," debate","."," While"," some"," argue"," that"," raising"," the"," requirement"," from"," a"," C"," average"," to"," a"," B"," average"," would"," increase"," academic"," accountability"," and"," foster"," a"," stronger"," work"," ethic"," among"," adolescents",","," I"," firmly"," believe"," that"," this"," proposed"," change"," would"," have"," negative"," repercussions"," and"," should"," not"," be"," implemented",".","\n","First"," and"," foremost",","," it"," is"," essential"," to"," acknowledge"," the"," potential"," impact"," of"," this"," change"," on"," adolescents","'"," mental"," health","."," By"," raising"," the"," grade"," point"," average"," requirement",","," students"," may"," face"," additional"," pressure"," to"," maintain"," high"," grades"," in"," order"," to"," participate"," in"," sports"," and"," extracurricular"," activities","."," This"," added"," stress"," can"," lead"," to"," anxiety",","," burnout",","," and"," a"," decline"," in"," overall"," well","-","being","."," Adoles","cents"," already"," face"," numerous"," academic"," and"," social"," pressures",","," and"," increasing"," the"," grade"," point"," average"," requirement"," would"," only"," exacerbate"," these"," challenges",","," potentially"," leading"," to"," negative"," outcomes",".","\n","Moreover",","," implementing"," a"," B"," average"," requirement"," may"," unfairly"," disadvantage"," students"," who"," excel"," in"," sports"," or"," extracurricular"," activities"," but"," struggle"," academically","."," Not"," all"," students"," possess"," the"," same"," aptitude"," for"," various"," subjects",","," and"," measuring"," their"," worth"," solely"," based"," on"," their"," grade"," point"," average"," could"," be"," an"," unfair"," assessment","."," By"," excluding"," these"," students"," from"," participating"," in"," activities"," they"," are"," passionate"," about",","," we"," risk"," demo","tiv","ating"," them"," and"," hindering"," their"," personal"," growth"," and"," development",".","\n","Furthermore",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," recognize"," the"," valuable"," skills"," and"," experiences"," that"," sports"," and"," extracurricular"," activities"," provide","."," Participation"," in"," these"," activities"," fosters"," teamwork",","," discipline",","," leadership",","," and"," time"," management"," skills","."," These"," are"," qualities"," that"," can"," contribute"," to"," a"," well","-","rounded"," individual"," and"," future"," success","."," By"," implementing"," a"," B"," average"," requirement",","," we"," risk"," depriving"," students"," of"," these"," important"," opportunities"," for"," personal"," growth"," and"," character"," development",".","\n","In"," conclusion",","," changing"," the"," grade"," point"," average"," requirement"," from"," a"," C"," average"," to"," a"," B"," average"," for"," sports"," and"," extracurricular"," activities"," would"," have"," negative"," implications"," for"," adolescents","."," It"," could"," lead"," to"," increased"," pressure"," and"," stress",","," unfairly"," disadvantage"," certain"," students",","," and"," limit"," opportunities"," for"," personal"," growth","."," Instead",","," we"," should"," focus"," on"," finding"," ways"," to"," support"," and"," motivate"," students"," academically"," while"," still"," recognizing"," the"," value"," of"," sports"," and"," extracurricular"," activities"," in"," their"," overall"," development","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}